author: jameskosin
msg: Added the TokenNameFinderDictionaryCreatorTool to the project.
This tool takes a US Census name file, currently in the old format with a space after the name and generates a usable dictionary from the input file.
This may help later with improving the name-finder in the future with a large sample of real names... at least everyone hopes they are all real names.
